## Command line

When invoking Python, you may specify any of these options:

```
python [-bBdEhiIOqsSuvVWx?] [-c command | -m module-name | script | - ] [args]
```

### Interface options

> Also refer to [Top-level components](https://github.com/wangzhenj321/Python-Manual/blob/master/blog/the_python_language_reference/toplevel_components/toplevel-components.md).

- `-c <command>`

    

- `-m <module-name>`

- `-`

- `<script>`
